               <code code="34071-1" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="WARNINGS SECTION"/>
               <title>Warning:</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content>a) Do not swallow b) Do not eat, drink or rinse with water for 30 minutes after use. c) Instruct children under 12 years of age in the use of the product and in good brushing and rinsing habits to minimize swallowing d) Not recommended for use in children younger than 6 years of age.</content>
